1
V wl aber d klen vogele n=
gen dc t war he ne nht lan=
ger n alo wl d lede wter 
twng ellu ar leht blvmen 
chn ch enkan dem walde nht en gru=

2
o mn og alrert erah wol d zt
dc wc mn gemach do as ch r vnd 
hte nah dc mr t nem mer gechach
we hee des vagte ch do ach balde 
chone ete o e lger o e leb got r lone
alo hat mr gennet ch
3
dc ands em leb were dne mr an=

4

5

zergan o we led v der trub zt da v

13

19
